<main>
    <article class="policy-wrap">
        <h1>{{ page.title | default: 'Shipping &amp; Delivery Policy' }}</h1>
        <p class="policy-lead">At Avyen, we aim to deliver your haircare ritual safely and smoothly across Pakistan.</p>

        <section class="policy-section">
            <h2>Delivery Time</h2>
            <p>Orders are usually delivered within 3–5 working days, depending on your city and courier service availability.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="policy-section">
            <h2>Delivery Areas</h2>
            <p>We deliver across Pakistan.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="policy-section">
            <h2>Delivery Charges</h2>
            <p>Delivery charges, if any, will be shown at checkout. If free delivery is active during an offer, it will be clearly mentioned on the website.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="policy-section">
            <h2>Cash on Delivery</h2>
            <p>Cash on Delivery is available for eligible orders across Pakistan.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="policy-section">
            <h2>Order Confirmation</h2>
            <p>Our team may contact you via call or WhatsApp to confirm your order before dispatch.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="policy-section">
            <h2>Delivery Issues</h2>
            <p>If your parcel is delayed, damaged, or not received, please contact Avyen Care through WhatsApp or email at <a href="mailto:avyenofficial@gmail.com">avyenofficial@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </section>
    </article>
</main>

